title: Watch the Northern Lights from your lawn
description: The cottage is rather small but the scenery is grand! If your stay is during the right time, you will see the amazing Aurora Borealis right from your lawn. Other than that, this cosy cottage in the middle of the forest is the perfect place to just be yourself for a while - alone with your thoughts and with no one to disturb your visit to the outhouse.
